<figureCitation box="[159,259,1453,1477]" captionStart="FIGURES 111–115" captionStartId="68.[151,264,1816,1839]" captionTargetBox="[198,1388,193,1795]" captionTargetId="figure-72@68.[198,1388,193,1795]" captionTargetPageId="68" captionText="FIGURES 111–115. Holotypes, ♀, lateral. 111, Debilos masipum sp. nov. 112, D. sanimum sp. nov. 113, D. tasamunum sp. nov. 114, D. curtuvenatum sp. nov. 115, D. xanthochrosatum sp. nov. Illustrations not to scale." pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Figs 115</figureCitation>
